article.description: — Payton Willis had 17 points as College of Charleston topped Delaware 66-59 on Sunday.
article.headline: Willis lifts Coll. Of Charleston over Delaware 66-59
article.linkText: Willis lifts Coll. Of Charleston over Delaware 66-59
article.story: NEWARK, Del. -- — Payton Willis had 17 points as College of Charleston topped Delaware 66-59 on Sunday. Zep Jasper added 13 points for the Cougars (3-6, 1-1 Colonial Athletic Association) and Cameron Copeland chipped in 10 points. Ryan Allen had 17 points for the Blue Hens (3-4, 1-1). Dylan Painter added 15 points and eight rebounds. Johnny McCoy had seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
